## Option 2 — Commercial License

**Use this option if:**
- You are a commercial entity building closed-source products
- You want to use the Work in proprietary hardware without open-sourcing
  your derivative work
- You want warranty, indemnification, and support
- You want access to source code updates and bug fixes

**Terms:** The Commercial License is available from the author under
separate agreement. Contact:

```
Adhiraj
[Your LLP Name]
Email: adhiraj@[your-domain]
Web:   https://[your-domain]/commercial-license
```

**What the Commercial License includes:**
- ✅ Right to use the Work in closed-source commercial products
- ✅ No obligation to open-source derivative works
- ✅ Warranty against IP infringement
- ✅ Indemnification against third-party IP claims
- ✅ 12 months of bug fixes and minor updates
- ✅ Priority email support
- ✅ Access to verification testbenches and regression suite
- ✅ Right to request custom modifications (at additional cost)

**Pricing models available:**
1. **Perpetual License + Royalty**: One-time fee + per-unit royalty
2. **Annual Subscription**: Yearly fee, includes updates
3. **Source Code Buyout**: One-time fee for full source + rights
4. **Evaluation License**: 90-day free eval (under NDA)

Contact the author for current pricing.

